      <div class="card-grid">
        <a href="/answers/aeo/does-answer-engine-consulting-offer-audits-or-pilot-engagements" class="answer-card">
          <h3>Audits and pilot engagements</h3>
          <p>Yes. The Starter package functions as a structured audit and pilot — delivering an answer gap analysis, structured data implementation, and a baseline AI visibility report. It is scoped and priced specifically to let organizations validate AEO impact before committing to ongoing investment.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/answers/aeo/how-is-aeo-different-from-hiring-an-seo-agency" class="answer-card">
          <h3>How is AEO different from hiring an SEO agency?</h3>
          <p>AEO and traditional SEO agencies target different outcomes: SEO agencies optimize for Google rankings and organic traffic; AEO optimizes for AI citations in LLM-generated responses. The content architecture, structured data requirements, and success metrics are fundamentally different.</p>
